Wednesday, June 10, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

91-2513. State ex rel. Lester v. Butler Cty.

Court of Common Pleas, Div. of Domestic Relations. Butler County, No. CA91-05-080. On joint motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
